column2: "If you're planning on continuing from here, then I suggest waiting a second. I'm not going to stop you."
"Don't worry, that's an ARKS member doing that. She should get bored and go home in a second."
"Really that old hag doesn't know the meaning of restraint. It's not like I have anything to do with her anyways."
"Seems like the sound stopped. It's probably safe now. Later."
